 Galvatron smiled. "still got you." His jewel power went off and sent a 2 
feet wide energy shot. he let go and grabbed the bots foot and pulled her out 
of the bots hand. he jetesened off.  God Neptune picked up Dark MOuse and 
flew off towards the base. Galvatron sent a comm to Guieldart. "get ready for 
possible attack." he put a small sedative in the cat bot to make sure she 
stayed asleep.
